AttributeList.Text: ================================================================================ This module is used everywhere 10 alarms has to be generated when one (security) corresponding input becomes True. All alarms can be True only when the corresponding input Enable Alarm is also True. When the conditions to generate the alarm is disappear, a boolean (one per alarm) available to inform the upper level that the corresponding alarm can be reset. All alarms are reset by means of the AlarmResetPB signal. ================================================================================
